Class GcmInstance

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.app.Service
      • com.google.android.gms.iid.InstanceIDListenerService
        • com.ucsf.core_phone.services.GcmInstance

  • public class GcmInstance
extends com.google.android.gms.iid.InstanceIDListenerService
    Service responsible of maintaining the validity of GCM tokens. GCM protocol is used to communicate with the server, more precisely to receive message from the server.
